<h1><a name="begin_content"></a>Audit (A-03-10-03105)</h1>

<h2>05-31-2011<br />
Appropriations Funding for National Institutes of Health Office of Research Facilities Development and Operations Contract C2000326 With Higgins Development Partners, LLC </h2>

<h2>Executive Summary</h2>


<p>Our review found that during fiscal years 2002 through 2009, NIH's Office of Research Facilities Development and Operations (ORF) funded contract C2000326 (the Contract), totaling $2.2 million (subsequently increased to $106.4 million), with Higgins Development Partners, LLC, in compliance with the purpose, time, and amount requirements specified in appropriations statutes.  ORF had a bona fide need for the services and materials and appropriately funded the Contract with no-year appropriations and annual appropriations from fiscal years 2002 through 2009.  </p>

<p>This report contains no recommendations.</p>


